---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Thank You - Rocky Horror Picture Show 2025">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section
    class="scroll-section position-relative min-vh-100 d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center overflow-hidden"
  >
    <!-- Background with animated gradient -->
    <div
      class="position-absolute top-0 start-0 w-100 h-100 bg-rhps-gradient animate-pulse"
    >
    </div>
    <img
      src="./images/noun-rocky-horror-681055.svg"
      alt="The Rocky Horror Picture Show Background"
      class="position-absolute top-0 start-0 w-100 h-100"
      style="opacity: 0.3;"
    />

    <!-- Content -->
    <div
      class="position-relative container"
      style="z-index: 10; padding-top: 75px;"
    >
      <div class="text-center mb-5">
        <h1 class="font-malicious-moonlight display-1 mb-0 text-rhps-gold">
          THANK YOU
        </h1>
        <p class="fs-3 mb-0">For an Amazing 25th Anniversary Season</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- To the Cast Section -->
  <section class="py-5" id="to-our-cast">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row g-5 mb-5">
        <h2
          class="font-malicious-moonlight display-3 fw-bold mb-4 text-rhps-gold"
        >
          To Our Incredible Cast
        </h2>
        <div class="col-md-8">
          <p class="fs-4 lh-lg mb-3">
            Your passion, dedication, and extraordinary talent brought this 25th
            anniversary production to life in ways we never imagined possible.
          </p>
          <p class="fs-4 lh-lg mb-3">
            You committed countless hours to perfecting every line, every dance
            move, and every moment of performance. Through late-night
            rehearsals, costume fittings, and endless character development,
            you've created something truly magical.
          </p>
          <p class="fs-4 lh-lg mb-3">
            Your energy on stage was infectious, your chemistry undeniable, and
            your commitment to honoring this beloved show while making it your
            own was nothing short of inspiring.
          </p>
          <p class="fs-4 lh-lg mb-4 text-rhps-gold fw-bold">
            Thank you for making this year unforgettable. You are the heart and
            soul of this production.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <div
            class="rounded p-4 border border-2 border-rhps-gold"
            style="background-color: #1a1a1a;"
          >
            <div class="text-center mb-4">
              <img
                src="./images/noun-fishnet-stockings-white-1154871.svg"
                alt="Cast Icon"
                style="height: 8rem; opacity: 0.8;"
              />
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="fs-3 text-center text-rhps-gold fw-bold mb-0">
            "Time is fleeting"<br />
            but your impact is everlasting.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- To the Audiences Section -->
  <section
    class="py-5 bg-rhps-gradient"
    style="min-height: 100vh;"
    id="to-our-audiences"
  >
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row g-5">
        <h2
          class="font-malicious-moonlight display-3 fw-bold mb-4 text-rhps-gold"
        >
          To Our Amazing Audiences
        </h2>
        <div class="col-md-8 order-md-2">
          <p class="fs-4 lh-lg mb-3">
            You didn't just come to watch a show—you came to be part of it. Your
            enthusiasm, your costumes, your participation, and your energy
            transformed every performance into something extraordinary.
          </p>
          <p class="fs-4 lh-lg mb-3">
            From the first-time "virgins" experiencing Rocky Horror for the very
            first time to the seasoned veterans who know every line, every
            callback, and every song—each of you brought something special to
            the theater.
          </p>
          <p class="fs-4 lh-lg mb-3">
            Your toast, your rice, your dancing in the aisles, and your
            infectious energy created an atmosphere that reminded us all why
            Rocky Horror continues to captivate audiences after 50 years.
          </p>
          <p class="fs-4 lh-lg mb-4 text-rhps-gold fw-bold">
            Thank you for making this celebration so special. You are what makes
            Rocky Horror more than just a show—it's a community, a tradition,
            and a celebration of pure joy.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 order-md-1">
          <div
            class="rounded p-4 border border-2 border-rhps-gold"
            style="background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);"
          >
            <div class="text-center mb-4">
              <img
                src="./images/noun-toast-white-8049484.svg"
                alt="Audience Icon"
                style="height: 8rem; opacity: 0.8;"
              />
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="fs-3 text-center text-rhps-gold fw-bold mb-0">
            "Don't dream it, be it!"<br />
            And you were!
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Special Thanks Section -->
  <section class="py-5" id="special-thanks">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-10">
          <div
            class="rounded p-5 border border-2 border-rhps-gold"
            style="background-color: #1a1a1a;"
          >
            <h2
              class="font-malicious-moonlight display-4 fw-bold mb-4 text-center text-rhps-gold"
            >
              Special Thanks
            </h2>
            <div class="row g-4">
              <div class="col-md-6">
                <h3 class="fs-4 fw-bold mb-3 text-rhps-gold">
                  Production Team
                </h3>
                <p class="text-light mb-4">
                  To everyone working tirelessly behind the scenes—from stage
                  management to costume design, lighting to sound, props to
                  makeup—thank you for bringing the vision to life.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-6">
                <h3 class="fs-4 fw-bold mb-3 text-rhps-gold">
                  The Kenworthy Theatre
                </h3>
                <p class="text-light mb-4">
                  Thank you for being our home and for providing a beautiful
                  space where our community could come together to celebrate
                  this iconic show year after year.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-6">
                <h3 class="fs-4 fw-bold mb-3 text-rhps-gold">Our Supporters</h3>
                <p class="text-light mb-4">
                  To our families, friends, and sponsors—your support makes all
                  of this possible. Thank you for believing in us and in the
                  magic of Rocky Horror.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-6">
                <h3 class="fs-4 fw-bold mb-3 text-rhps-gold">
                  The Rocky Horror Community
                </h3>
                <p class="text-light mb-4">
                  To everyone who has ever been touched by Rocky Horror anywhere
                  in the world—you've kept this tradition alive for 50 years,
                  and we're honored to be part of it.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Looking Forward Section -->
  <section class="py-5 bg-rhps-gradient">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-8 text-center">
          <h2
            class="font-malicious-moonlight display-3 fw-bold mb-4 text-rhps-gold"
          >
            Until Next Time
          </h2>
          <p class="fs-3 lh-lg mb-4">
            As we close the curtain on our 25th anniversary year, we carry with
            us the memories of incredible performances, unforgettable audiences,
            and the joy that only Rocky Horror can bring.
          </p>
          <p class="fs-3 lh-lg mb-5">
            We couldn't have done it without each and every one of you. Thank
            you for being part of this amazing journey.
          </p>
          <p class="fs-2 text-rhps-gold fw-bold mb-0">
            "Let's do the Time Warp again!"
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer class="py-5 border-top border-rhps-gold">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <p class="fs-5 mb-3">
        <span class="text-rhps-gold fw-bold"
          >The Rocky Horror Picture Show Experience at The Kenworthy</span
        >
      </p>
      <p class="mb-3">25th Anniversary Production • October 24-25, 2025</p>
      <p class="small">"Don't dream it, be it!" - Dr. Frank-N-Furter</p>
      <p class="small">Copyright 2025, Sirius Entertainment</p>
      <!-- <p class="small mt-3">
        <a href="/" class="text-light text-decoration-underline"
          >← Back to Home</a
        >
      </p> -->
    </div>
  </footer>
</Layout>
